{"id":20350,"date":"2015-02-12T19:33:18","date_gmt":"2015-02-12T15:33:18","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=20350"},"modified":"2019-05-20T18:25:47","modified_gmt":"2019-05-20T14:25:47","slug":"hasan-on-kharijites-dunya","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/02\/12\/hasan-on-kharijites-dunya\/","title":{"rendered":"Hasan on Khawarij: Rebels fight for sake of the world, not Islam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Hayyan al-Tawhidi reported: A man from the Khawarij came to Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, and he said, \u201cWhat do you say about the rebels?\u201d Hasan said, \u201cThey are seekers of the world.\u201d The man said, \u201cWhy do you say that when one of them goes out with his spear until it breaks and he leaves his family and children?\u201d Hasan said, \u201cTell me about the ruler. Does he prevent you from establishing prayer, giving charity, and performing the pilgrimage?\u201d The man said no. Hasan said, \u201cAs I see it, he has only prevented you from seeking the world and you have fought him for it.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Bas\u0323a\u0304&#8217;ir wal-Dhakha\u0304&#8217;ir\u00a01\/34<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062d\u064a\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u062d\u064a\u062f\u064a \u0623\u062a\u0649 \u0631\u062c\u0644 \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0648\u0627\u0631\u062c \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0641\u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0644\u0647 \u0645\u0627 \u062a\u0642\u0648\u0644 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0648\u0627\u0631\u062c \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0647\u0645 \u0623\u0635\u062d\u0627\u0628 \u062f\u0646\u064a\u0627 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0648\u0645\u0646 \u0623\u064a\u0646 \u0642\u0644\u062a \u0648\u0623\u062d\u062f\u0647\u0645 \u064a\u0645\u0634\u064a \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0645\u062d \u062d\u062a\u0649 \u